      • condition

        public boolean condition​(TContainer container,
                         T agent)
        [Visible if agents are dropped off While condition is true] Condition evaluated for each agent in the container to determine whether it should be picked up. The condition expression may depend on the contanter agent as well as on the "candidate" to be dropped off.

        Parameters:
        T agent - the agent to be dropped off.
        TContainer container - the container agent.
